@DATABASE "Ghosts 'N' Goblins"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - G - Ghosts 'N' Goblins"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - G
                   ====================================

                            Ghosts 'N' Goblins
                            ==================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(36057,182)"}          36057,182
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(25177,255) zxampoke(49047,255)"}          25177,x:49047,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
